==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sexennial
<hw>Sex*en"ni*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sexennium</ets> a period of six years, <ets>sexennis</ets> of six
years; <ets>sex</ets> six + <ets>annus</ets> a year. See <er>Six</er>,
and <er>Annual</er>.]</ety> <def>Lasting six years, or happening once in
six years.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A sexennial
event.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sexennially</ent>⟦br⟧
